caption.text:
Followers DO NOT equal sales…

I’ve seen so many creators with hundreds of thousands of followers make only a few hundred dollars.

The main reason is because they only focus on views.

When you only focus on views you create broad, dumbed down content that doesn’t showcase your expertise or establish trust.

If you can’t establish any trust you will hardly make any sales.

To establish this trust and get followers at the same time you need to have a content funnel.

This funnel will convert casual viewers into ready-to-buy customers.

If you want help turning your viewers into consistent cash DM me “IN” and I’ll how I can help you.

#contentmarketingtips #contentmarketing #contentstrategy #contentwriting #socialmediamarketing
